{"tid":275597,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【旺角騷亂】警長稱手因擋磚而受傷 醫療報告指是跌傷","createTime":"2017-06-08T06:56:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T10:51:08.000Z","uid":8883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3b524ea13272e180402e0fe3481550a16ab4dd3e","tid":275597,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T06:56:35.000Z","msg":"去年大年初二凌晨旺角發生的騷亂，事後多人被控以暴動罪，其中涉及9名男子的案件今續審。案發時為總督察的現任警司陳偉基供稱，其左手當日因擋磚而受傷，但被辯方質疑指其醫療報告是註明他是跌傷，陳表示不知原因。<br />\n<br />\n控方在庭上播放當日的新聞片段，以及中銀的閉路電視片段，看到陳偉基被磚掟中後流血。陳指在拘捕第六被告後現場開始平靜，否則若他及警長黃樂安再中磚會有「更嚴重受傷，死亡都唔出奇」。<br />\n<br />\n而辯方指第六被告陳和祥(71歲)當日是剛步出行人隧道便被制服，被告根本沒有掟磚，惟陳指目擊第六被告有掟磚，之後見警方開始拘捕掟磚者後，便用龜速跑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170608&amp;guid=56800077&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170608%26guid%3D56800077%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=Q2Uo%2BPiB9%2B0hyObms5P5VwKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=9bea7c74\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170608%26guid%3D56800077%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=44f76740\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170608&amp;guid=56800077&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"ee0702e93302aa7c945451e31997e5bb03f55b80","tid":275597,"uid":22313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T07:21:50.000Z","msg":"妨礙司法公正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"761498d931ff1f24e786b7117e2418bba32a64b5","tid":275597,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T07:26:56.000Z","msg":"地下都係磚<br />\n跌落地攞手擋都係擋磚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"883ebfc3f31f358cc419b6775448f3a0b3a903eb","tid":275597,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T0